    <item>
      <title>拉加德说，欧盟必须接受多数投票对否决权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/lagarde-says-eu-must-embrace-majority-voting-over-veto-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲中央银行总裁克里斯汀·拉加德（Christine Lagarde）呼吁对欧盟的决定进行大修，并提议应接受多数投票，以使集团更具竞争力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/lagarde-says-eu-must-embrace-majority-voting-over-veto-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 19:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街敦促IPO希望在弱市场中估算估值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/wall-street-urges-ipo-hopefuls-to-trim-valuations-in-weak-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于动荡不安的美国股票市场乌云密布，因此，华尔街的一些人敦促公司敦促他们进行估值，以便有更好的机会取得成功的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/wall-street-urges-ipo-hopefuls-to-trim-valuations-in-weak-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 19:43:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西门子以51亿美元的价格购买洞察力的杂货店</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/siemens-is-said-to-near-deal-for-insight-backed-dotmatics</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Siemens AG已同意以51亿美元的价格收购Dotmatics，这是为生命科学公司提供更多人工智能软件的推动力的一部分。]]></description>
