    <item>
      <title>SmartStop自存储REIT在8.1亿美元IPO之后攀升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/smartstop-self-storage-reit-advances-after-810-million-us-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[SmartStop Self Storage REIT Inc.在自存储房地产投资信托基金（Self Storage Real Estate Investment Trust）在首次公开募股中筹集了8.1亿美元之后，获得了市场的首次亮相，并将其股票在销售范围的下半年定价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/smartstop-self-storage-reit-advances-after-810-million-us-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 17:03:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
